### Why Erlang? WhatsApp Secret Weapon

WhatsApp chose **Erlang/OTP** because of the BEAM VM unique properties:

| Feature | Benefit for WhatsApp |
|---------|---------------------|
| Lightweight processes | 2KB per process, millions per server |
| Preemptive scheduling | Fair CPU sharing across millions of connections |
| Hot code reloading | Deploy without disconnecting users |
| Built-in distribution | Nodes communicate natively |
| Let it crash philosophy | Fault isolation per connection |

Each WhatsApp connection is an Erlang process. A single server handles **2M+ concurrent connections**.

